</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<div class="stat-dot"></div>
<div class="stat-title">Strengthen</div>
<div class="stat-text">Improve controls, configurations, and defensive posture.</div>
</div>

<div class="stat-card">
<div class="stat-dot"></div>
<div class="stat-title">Support</div>
<div class="stat-text">Provide practical guidance built around real business needs.</div>
</div>
</div>

</div>
</div>

</section>

<section id="services" class="section">
<div class="section-header">
<h2 class="section-title">Services</h2>
<p class="section-text">Security support designed to help small businesses improve visibility, reduce exposure, and strengthen resilience against modern cyber threats.</p>
</div>

<div class="grid-3">

<div class="card">
<div class="card-icon"></div>
<h3>Threat Monitoring & Visibility</h3>
<p>Review signs of suspicious activity, improve awareness of possible exposure, and help identify indicators that may warrant deeper investigation.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<div class="card-icon"></div>
